  "local_port": 57024,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Which online coaching institute is best for CAT Preparation?",
  "response": "Choosing the best online coaching institute for CAT preparation depends on several factors, including your learning style, budget, and specific needs. However, here are some of the most popular and highly regarded online coaching institutes for CAT preparation:\n\n---\n\n### **1. IMS (Institute of Management Studies)**  \n- **Highlights**:  \n   - Proven track record with experienced faculty.  \n   - Comprehensive study material and mock tests.  \n   - Personalized mentorship programs.  \n   - Regularly updated content based on CAT trends.  \n- **Website**: [IMS India](https://www.imsindia.com/)\n\n---\n\n### **2. TIME (Triumphant Institute of Management Education)**  \n- **Highlights**:  \n   - Trusted name in CAT coaching with a strong offline and online presence.  \n   - Extensive test series and detailed analysis.  \n   - Focus on conceptual clarity and problem-solving techniques.  \n- **Website**: [TIME](https://www.time4education.com/)\n\n---\n\n### **3. Career Launcher**  \n- **Highlights**:  \n   - One of the oldest and most reputed institutes for CAT preparation.  \n   - Offers a blend of live classes and recorded sessions.  \n   - Robust mock test series with detailed performance analysis.  \n   - Dedicated doubt-solving sessions.  \n- **Website**: [Career Launcher](https://www.careerlauncher.com/)\n\n---\n\n### **4. Byju's CAT Prep**  \n- **Highlights**:  \n   - Interactive video lessons and adaptive learning modules.  \n   - Flexible learning schedules.  \n   - Personalized mentorship and test series.  \n   - Focus on AI-driven analytics for performance improvement.  \n- **Website**: [Byju's](https://byjus.com/cat/)\n\n---\n\n### **5. CL (Cracku)**  \n- **Highlights**:  \n   - Affordable and flexible courses.  \n   - Strong focus on quality mock tests and sectional tests.  \n   - Daily practice questions and video solutions.  \n   - Mobile-friendly app for convenient learning.  \n- **Website**: [Cracku](https://cracku.in/)\n\n---\n\n### **6. TestFunda (by Disha Education)**  \n- **Highlights**:  \n   - Detailed study material and video lessons.  \n   - Regular webinars by CAT toppers and experts.  \n   - Adaptive tests to track progress.  \n   - Affordable pricing compared to competitors.  \n- **Website**: [TestFunda](https://www.testfunda.com/)\n\n---\n\n### **7. Unacademy**  \n- **Highlights**:  \n   - Wide range of courses by experienced educators.  \n   - Live interactive classes and recorded sessions.  \n   - Affordable subscription plans.  \n   - Focus on all sections of CAT: QA, VARC, and DILR.  \n- **Website**: [Unacademy](https://unacademy.com/)\n\n---\n\n### **8. 98th Percentile**  \n- **Highlights**:  \n   - Focuses on personalized learning and mentorship.  \n   - Regularly updated study material and mock tests.  \n   - Affordable pricing with flexible schedules.  \n   - Consistently good student reviews.  \n- **Website**: [98th Percentile](https://www.98thpercentile.com/)\n\n---\n\n### **How to Choose the Right Institute?**  \n- **Evaluate Faculty**: Look for experienced and reputed faculty members.  \n- **Study Material**: Ensure the study material is comprehensive and updated.  \n- **Mock Tests**: A robust mock test series is crucial for CAT preparation.  \n- **Reviews and Success Stories**: Check student reviews and past results.  \n- **Budget**: Compare pricing and choose one that fits your budget.  \n- **Free Trials**: Many platforms offer free trials or demo classes\u2014take advantage of these to assess the quality.  \n\n---\n\nUltimately, the \"best\" institute is the one that aligns with your learning needs and helps you achieve your CAT goals.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
